<p><span style="font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif">Ahead of the next meeting, could you please partner with Alexis to make sure the following is done:</span><o:p></o:p></p>
<p><span style="font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></p>
