 storefront urls for redirects).</span><o:p></o:p></li><li class="xmsonormal" style="mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><span style="font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif">Share conversion data for our keywords from Adobe.</span><o:p></o:p></li></ol>
